snippet.title: World to the West Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more at: http://www.worldtothewest.com

World to the West is an action puzzler that continues exploring the universe of Teslagrad, already started by over 1.6 million people. Discover a world of corrupt colonies and forgotten civilizations. Play as four characters, each with their own unique abilities, to explore untamed jungles, frozen tundras and an ancient prophecy. Be careful though. Nothing is ever what it seems. 

Follow World to the West
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/World-to-the-West-980084578743909/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WorldToTheWest
Website: www.worldtothewest.com
